summary: A mod that adds a tree with some epic loot. Only the most hardy of adventurers can claim it.
descriptionHtml: This mod adds a majestic pine tree towering over the landscape of Whiterun. Only true adventurers can make it to the root of the tree, and claim the magical blossom staff. The path is perilous however, for the tree is guarded by many grotesque creatures (like bears and naked women). Only the most hardy can make it.
author: Morpheel
